<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Lab Test Cancellation – Service Provider Notification</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color:
      #f7f9fb; margin: 0; padding: 20px; color: #333; } .email-box { max-width:
      650px; margin: auto; background: #ffffff; padding: 25px; border-radius:
      10px; box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); } .header {
      background-color: #dc3545; color: white; padding: 18px; border-radius:
      8px; text-align: center; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; } .footer {
      margin-top: 25px; font-size: 13px; color: #777; text-align: center; }
      .highlight { color: #dc3545; font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>

    <div class="email-box">

      <div class="header">
        Lab Test Cancellation Notification
      </div>

      <p>Dear {{labName}},</p>

      <p>
        This is to inform you that the lab test booked by
        <strong>{{customerName}}</strong>
        has been
        <span class="highlight">cancelled</span>.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you have any concerns or need clarification, feel free to reach out
        to the Mobilab2u team.
      </p>

      <p>Thank you for your cooperation.</p>

      <p>Best regards,<br />
        The Mobilab2u Team</p>

      <div class="footer">
        ©
        {{currentYear}}
        Mobilab2u. All rights reserved.
      </div>

    </div>

  </body>
</html>